results.Content: Hi, Broncos. Thanks for calling City Cabs. To book a taxi for now, press 1. To prebook a taxi, press 2. For account booking
Great. If the pickup location is New Town Deli, 23 Henderson Row EH3. If the drop off location is New Town Deli, 42 Broughton Street EH1, press 1. Otherw--

Thanks. I have scheduled your booking. If you'd like to provide additional instructions for your driver, press 1. If you would like to schedule a return booking for later, press 2. Your driver will be on the way shortly to pick you up from New Town Deli. Goodbye, and see you soon.
